race.comment: Competitive. TOP ARCTIC (2) is third-up and can find his best with the step up in trip. Needs some luck pushing forward but she races well here and the 2kg claim is handy. OUTCASTER (9) got well back and ran below expectations last time at Stony Creek over 2100m. Had just missed this distance range at Yarra Valley prior and 3x winning rider Noonan is reunited, replacing the 2kg apprentice. Draws inside and should get every chance. UNQUESTIONABLY (3) comes out of the same contest at Stony Creek beaten 1.5 lengths as favourite. Made sharp improvement and he also has winning claims. TRACK PATCHER (5) out of the same race peaks and is capable of better.
